\v 10 Yediael's¦190785 son was Bilhan. Bilhan's¦190786 sons were Yeush¦190789, Benyamin¦190791, Ehud¦190792, Kenaanah¦190793, Zetan¦190794, Tarshish¦190795, and Ahishahar¦190796.
