\rem /s1 Asher; The Descendants of Asher
\p
\v 30 Asher's¦191051 sons¦191050 were Yimnah, Yishvah, Yishvi, and Beriah¦191055. Their sister¦191057 was Serah¦191056.
\p
\v 31 Beriah's¦191060 sons¦191059 were Hever and¦191062 Malkiel. Malkiel was the father¦191064 of Birzayit.
\p
\v 32 Heber was the father¦191069 of Yaflet¦191072, Shomer¦191075, Hotam¦191078, and their¦191081 sister¦191081 Shua¦191080.
\v 33 Yaflet's¦191084 sons were Pasak, Bimhal¦191086, and Ashvat¦191087.
\p
\v 34 Shomer's sons¦191092 were Ahi¦191094, Rohgah¦191095, Hubbah, and Aram¦191099.
\p
\v 35 \add Shomer's younger\add* brother was Helem. Helem's¦191103 sons¦191101 were Tsofah, Yimna, Shelesh¦191107, and Amal¦191108.
\p
\v 36 Zofah's¦191111 sons¦191110 were Suah¦191112, Harnefer¦191113, Shual¦191114, Beri¦191115, Yimrah¦191116,
\v 37 Betser, Hod¦191119, Shamma¦191120, Shilshah¦191121, Yitran (whose other name was Yeter), and Beera¦191123.
