\p
\v 13 plus Beriah and¦191292 Shema¦191292 who were leaders of their clans who lived in Ayyalon \add city\add*. They forced the people who lived in Gat¦191303 city to flee.
\v 14-16 Beriah's sons were Ahyo, Shashak¦191306, Yeremot, Zevadyah, Arad, Eder, Mikael, Yishpah, and¦191307 Yoha.
