\p
\v 17-18 \add Other\add* descendants of Elpaal were Zevadyah, Meshullam¦191320, Hizki¦191321, Heber¦191322, Yishmerai, Yizliah, and Yovav.
\p
\v 19-21 \add Another descendant of Benyamin was Shimei.\add* Shimei's descendants \add ≈included\add* Yakim, Zikri¦191331, Zavdi, Elienai, Tsilletai, Eliel, Adayah, Berayah, and Shimrat.
