\p
\v 33 Ner¦191419 was the father of Kish. Kish was the father of \add King\add* Shaul. Shaul was the father of Yonatan \add (Jonathan)\add*, Malki¦191436-Shua¦191438, Avinadav, and Esh-Baal.
\v 34 Yonatan's son was Meriv-Baal. Meriv-Baal was the father¦191453 of Mikah.
