\p
\v 14 From Levi's descendants \add who returned to Yehudah there were\add*: Shemayah¦191762 (Hasshuv's son, Hasshuv was Azrikam's¦191768 son, Azrikam was Hashavyah's son, Hashavyah was a descendant of \add Levi's youngest son\add* Merari¦191775),
\rem /s1 The Temple Guards Who Lived in Jerusalem
